verbose_text: Since the focus of this study was variation of CP4 EPSPS expression, the acute non toxic dose level of 572 mg/kg body weight and soybean consumption of 2.0 g/kg body weight / day were kept constant and only the protein expression variable was adjusted to illustrate the modest differences in MOE values associated with changes in protein expression levels in glyphosate-tolerant soybean across the broad dataset used in this study.
